<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>Chalkboard | Yet, Another DevApp</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/index.css">
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="button" id="viewer" onclick="window.location.href='/viewer';">
			<div>
				<h1 style="text-align: center">Viewer</h1>
				<hr />
				<h2>If you are going to join a session, click here. In the bar at the top of the page, please enter the session ID given to you!</h2>
				<hr />
				<img src="/viewer.png" class="img"></img>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="button" id="presenter" onclick="window.location.href='/presenter';">
			<div>
				<h1 style="text-align: center">Presenter</h1>
				<hr />
				<h2>Please click here if you want to broadcast using this service! Chalkboard provides an extremely simple, yet powerful interface, making it possible for you to rule your presentations. You can have as many users logged into the generated stream. They will all get to watch you paint along!</h2>
				<hr />
				<img src="/presenter.png" class="img"></img>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>